--------------------------- WEAPONS --------------------------------
ARES PREDATOR III
- Base Damage: 9P + net hits
- AP: -1 | APDS: -5 [SITUATIONAL: APDS ammo]
- Dice Pool: 17 [ALWAYS ACTIVE: Smartlink] [SITUATIONAL: Heavy Pistols spec]
- Mode: SA | Ammo: 15(c)

--------------------------- ARMOR ----------------------------------
ARMOR JACKET
- Base: 12 | +Ballistic Mask 2 = 14
- Soak: Body 5 + Armor 14 = 19 dice
- Average soak: 6-7 hits
- Note: AP reduces armor before soak

CHAMELEON SUIT
- Base: 9 | +Ballistic Mask 2 = 11
- Soak: Body 5 + Armor 11 = 16 dice
- +2 Sneaking [SITUATIONAL: CAMO ACTIVE]

--------------------------- COMBAT MECHANICS FLOW ------------------
1. ATTACK ROLL: Roll weapon skill pool vs. target's Dodge
2. NET HITS: Add net hits to weapon base damage
3. ARMOR PENETRATION: Subtract AP from target armor
4. SOAK ROLL: Target rolls Body + Effective Armor
5. FINAL DAMAGE: Base + net hits - soak hits

--------------------------- SITUATIONAL MODIFIERS ------------------
COMBAT:
- Cover, low-light, recoil, called shot, running [adjust per rules]

SOCIAL:
- First Impression, Social Chameleon, Physical leverage, Haggling, Con vs suspicious targets

STEALTH:
- Observers alert, half-speed, camo active

PERCEPTION:
- Distracted, Goggles, Earbuds, Hawk Eye

--------------------------- TAG GLOSSARY ---------------------------
[ALWAYS ACTIVE], [SITUATIONAL], [BASE], [UNTRAINED], [FIRST ENCOUNTER ONLY], [WHEN HAGGLING], [WHEN USING PHYSICAL LEVERAGE], [WHEN IMPERSONATING KNOWN PERSON], [WHEN IN URBAN ENVIRONMENT], [WHEN USING HEAVY PISTOL], [WHEN PICKING ELECTRONIC LOCKS], [WHEN USING TOOL KIT], [WHEN USING AUTOPICKER], [WHEN DECRYPTING], [WHEN USING AUDIO ENHANCEMENTS], [CAMO ACTIVE], [VISUAL ONLY], [STACKS: X], [AFFECTS: Y], [ESSENCE_COST: Z]

--------------------------- QUALITIES MECHANICAL SUMMARY -----------
- First Impression: +2 first social test [FIRST ENCOUNTER ONLY]
- Catlike: +2 Sneaking, +1 Physical limit [ALWAYS ACTIVE]
- Hawk Eye: +2 Visual Perception, +1 Visual limit [ALWAYS ACTIVE, VISUAL ONLY]
- Social Chameleon: +2 Impersonation, +1 Social limit [SITUATIONAL]
- Guts: +2 resist fear/intimidation [SITUATIONAL]
- Quick Healer: +2 to healing tests [SITUATIONAL]
- Lightning Reflexes: +1 REA, +1 dice Initiative, +1 dice defense [ALWAYS ACTIVE]

--------------------------- CYBERWARE MECHANICAL SUMMARY -----------
- Wired Reflexes 2: REA +2, +2d6 Initiative
- Tailored Pheromones 2: +2 all social skills
- Smartlink: +2 dice on smartgun weapons
- Datajack: direct neural interface, no dice bonus
